### Real LLM call
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: acme
X-Team-Id: engineering

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "What is a large language model in one sentence?" }
  ],
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
}

### Check request counter
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/ai.requests.total

### Check latency histogram
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/ai.request.latency

### Check  rejected counter
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/ai.requests.rejected

### acme gets 20 req/min (overridden)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/acme/usage

### trial gets only 3 req/min
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/trial/usage

### get a token from local auth server
POST http://localhost:8080/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic dGVuYW50LWdhdGV3YXktY2xpZW50OnNlY3JldA==
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials

### use token to call chat endpoint
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Say hello" }
  ],
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
}